### Commute API Test File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register a new user (to get a token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "faculty": "Engineering"
}

### 2. Login to get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Log a commute (Short distance - Car)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "Times Square, New York",
  "destination": "Central Park, New York",
  "transportType": "Car"
}

### 4. Log a commute (Short distance - Walk)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "White House, Washington DC",
  "destination": "Lincoln Memorial, Washington DC",
  "transportType": "Walk"
}

### 5. Log a commute (Medium distance - Bus)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "Boston, MA",
  "destination": "Cambridge, MA",
  "transportType": "Bus"
}

### 6. Log a commute (Long distance - Train)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "New York, NY",
  "destination": "Philadelphia, PA",
  "transportType": "Train"
}

### 7. Log a commute (Bike)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "Golden Gate Bridge, San Francisco",
  "destination": "Fisherman's Wharf, San Francisco",
  "transportType": "Bike"
}

### 8. Get commute history
GET {{baseUrl}}/commute/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get emission summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/commute/emission-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Test with invalid transport type (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "Los Angeles, CA",
  "destination": "San Diego, CA",
  "transportType": "Airplane"
}

### 11. Test without authentication (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/commute/history

### 12. Test with missing fields (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/commute/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startLocation": "Seattle, WA"
}
